title: Russell Simmons Presents Stand-Up at the El Rey
overview: Russell Simmons Presents Stand-Up at the El Rey, the unique stand-up show with a hip hop vibe, hosted by JB Smoove ("Curb Your Enthusiasm") will reflect the urban culture of today's youth through stand-up comedy. Each episode will consist of three up-and-coming comics and will feature music created by DJ Cassidy.
